xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pxo1665702742607.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pxo1665702742607.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pxo1665702742607.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pxo1665702742607\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__errordir_480448\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the path to the directory where language-specific sub-directories containing\n      web error message pages are located. The WRD servlet requires read access to these\n      directories.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__topic_d147395e1_d147396e1_d147397e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__p_d147398e1_d147399e1_d147400e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ERRORDIR</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorDirectory</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__p_d147401e1_d147402e1_d147403e1\">Default if omitted: Language directory within the web application, for example <span class=\"ph filepath\">WEB-INF</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__topic_d106237e1_d106238e1_d106239e1_d106240e1_d106241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d804468e79\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Usually, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">error_en</code> (English) and\n            other <code class=\"ph codeph\">error_Lang</code> directories are located in the web application\n            directory, which is located in the document tree of the web server.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"pxo1665702742607__note_N1004F_N10047_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This parameter has no effect in a\n      self-contained web application, which does not access folders or files outside of the virtual\n      root.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdq1665702742736.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Customize WRD Error Messages</a><p>Uniface provides a set of WRD error messages, which you can customize to your liking.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531126\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531126\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ERRORDIR Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the path to the directory where language-specific sub-directories containing web error message pages are located. The WRD servlet requires read access to these directories. <init-param> <param-name> ERRORDIR </param-name> <param-value> ErrorDirectory </param-value> </init-param> Default if omitted: Language directory within the web application, for example WEB-INF Description Usually, the error_en (English) and other error_Lang directories are located in the web application directory, which is located in the document tree of the web server. Note: This parameter has no effect in a self-contained web application, which does not access folders or files outside of the virtual root. Related Links Customize WRD Error Messages Uniface provides a set of WRD error messages, which you can customize to your liking. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}